<h1 class="font-bold text-2xl text-center" style="text-align: center">The Policy and Procedures of Partnership and Contracting with Emdad Platform Company</h1>

<p class="font-bold m-2 p-2"><strong>Preamble:</strong></p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    Emdad platform is a technical electronic platform designed to facilitate the process between the buyer and supplier, and to provide better and faster services. This can be carried out by registering on the platform and adhering to its terms and conditions that shall be mentioned later. When submitting a request for quotations by the buyer through the platform after filling the request information, they shall receive one or several quotations from multiple suppliers. Upon receiving quotation from suppliers, the buyer shall choose the supplier based on their preference, (i.e.  price, quality, etc.) After the selection and approval of the suitable supplier through the platform, the supplier shall provide the service, as agreed upon in the purchase order. The payment shall be either through credit, cash or pay on receipt by using credit cards (Mada - Visa - Apple Pay) or direct bank transfer. All financial payments sent to the supplier shall be first received in the bank account of Emdad Technical Platform Company. After confirming the information, the supply and receipt process, it will be transferred to the supplier’s account directly. Both, the buyer and supplier, shall acknowledge that Emdad Technical Platform Company is merely an intermediary party responsible for providing a direct communication service between the buyer and supplier to facilitate, speed up and support the supply chain process. Your success is ours, too!
</p>

<p class="font-bold m-2 p-2"><strong>Terminology:</strong></p>

<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Emdad platform:</strong> An electronic platform built with high experience to serve the seller and buyer in the procurement, sale, supply and storage process, with the lowest costs and the best technical and logistical standards.An electronic platform built with high experience to serve the seller and buyer in the procurement, sale, supply and storage process, with the lowest costs and the best technical and logistical standards.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Application, site or platform:</strong> A database or software process that has been fully programmed by Emdad platform with the best technical quality standards allowing its users to deal with (experience - speed - ease - security).
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Additional application:</strong> It is an application serves the platform (Emdad Tools) to be downloaded on mobile devices or smart devices to benefit from shipment tracking services or electronic approval, which is a free service for users of the platform. The same information and login data shall be used for the platform.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Buyer:</strong> Registered on the platform to benefit from its services to make requests, track shipments and receive quotations.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Supplier:</strong> Registered on the platform to benefit from its services to make quotations, schedule shipments, supply and delivery, and to provide their services.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>The first party:</strong> Emdad Platform Company.
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>The second party:</strong> The buyer.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Platform owner:</strong> Emdad Platform Company
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Commercial registration No.:</strong> 1010678061
</p>

<p class="font-bold m-2 p-2"><strong>Policy, conditions, and procedures of Emdad’s platform user:</strong></p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    Any use of the provided services by Emdad Platform Company shall be approved by this contract and its provisions. Accordingly, you shall not use the platform if you do not accept the policy and procedures of this contract. Emdad Platform Company shall have the right to modify or change the policy and procedures without prior notice. You shall be responsible, as a user of the platform, of reviewing the policy and procedures of use frequently. You can check and follow up with the updates by visiting the policy and procedures on the platform or by receiving an email from the Emdad’s platform team.
</p>

<p class="font-bold m-2 p-2"><strong>Acknowledgment of the buyer:</strong></p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    Using the platform by the buyer will be considered as an approval from the buyer and that he or she has read and understood the policy and procedures of this agreement and the manner of using the platform, application or site. It will be considered as an explicit consent from the buyer on the terms and conditions of this agreement and respond to it with full legal capacity.
    In case of acceptance, the terms and conditions of the agreement shall be considered valid between Emdad Platform Company and the buyer or supplier. All the obligations, Policy and procedures of this agreement shall be bound by the buyer and supplier, unless the context requires otherwise.
</p>

<p class="font-bold m-2 p-2"><strong>Eligibility for services:</strong></p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    The buyer shall acknowledge the following: <br>
    •	You have the full power and authority to sign a contract. Thus, you shall not be in breach of any law or fictitious contract.<br>
    •	You are an independent party and you do not act as an agent, representative, distributor, or investment partner of the Emdad Platform Company.<br>
    •	Your use of the company’s services ‘Emdad Platform Company’ has never been suspended or withhold at any time.<br>
    •	You are not a competitor to Emdad Platform Company, nor do you offer any product that competes with the services provided by Emdad Platform Company.<br>
    •	You shall not, directly or indirectly, present yourself as a representative of Emdad Platform Company, or act in a manner that may lead to some obligations without the prior written consent of Emdad Platform Company.<br>
    •	In case of approval, your privilege is restricted to the business that allows you to provide your services only. You shall have no right to make any offers to users on behalf of Emdad Platform Company. You acknowledge that your breach of this clause shall make you fully responsible for all obligations arising from this breach and expose you to criminal prosecution and prohibit your use of Emdad Platform Company.<br>
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Privacy policy of Emdad Platform Company:</strong> <br>
    •	All process, information, transactions and documents of Emdad Platform Company shall be extremely confidential and fully protected in a smart cloud and cannot be amended, deleted, or even viewed, except by government agencies or authorized entities.</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Approval and cancellation of purchase orders:</strong> <br>
    •	In case of using the platform while holding the first authority as a user, or the authority has been given to another user with authorization, this approval shall be considered official and bound on both parties (supplier and buyer). It can be only canceled through the consent of both parties.<br>
    •	The service buyer shall have the right, if the payment was in advance, to cancel the order and recover the paid amount when it becomes three days late to the specified date of supply in the approved purchase order.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>The purchase orders attached with a contracting formula:</strong> <br>
    •	Each of the (supplier and buyer) shall be bound by all the written regulations, terms and conditions in the attached contract, which only can be modified with the consent of the two parties through a request of amendment on the platform, using the icon (Request to amend the contract form). In the event that the other party agrees, the amendment shall be made and accepted by both parties and approved again.<br>
    •	Each of the (supplier and buyer) shall have the right to terminate the contract in the event that one of the parties does not abide by the regulations, terms and conditions agreed upon in the contract. The amendment shall be done by sending a request to terminate the contract with Emdad Platform Company using the icon (termination of the contract) and attaching the proof. Emdad platform team shall review the request and cancel it after confirming.<br>
    •	Each of the (supplier and buyer) shall have the right to terminate the contract at any time if both parties agreed.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Quotations Approval:</strong> <br>
    •	In the case of registering in and using the platform while holding the first authority as a user, or the authority has been given to another user, the approval of the quotation shall be official and mandatory on the supplier until its expiration date.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Supply and receipt:</strong> <br>
    •	The service buyer shall have the right to reject receiving the service or product if it does not conform to the specifications agreed upon in the purchase order or contract form.<br>
    •	The buyer shall be obligated to receive the approved service or shipment if it conforms to the approved specifications in the purchase order, unless it is three says late the agreed upon date.<br>
    •	The service buyer shall be obligated to receive on time. The supplier shall have the right to leave the service or product if the delay exceeds 15 minutes.<br>
    •	The supplier shall be obligated to be responsible for completing the delivery process and approving the receipt of the invoice before leaving the place of delivery electronically via the invoice number or scanning on the (Emdad Tools) application using smart phones.<br>
    •	The supplier shall be obligated to bear the shipping costs in the event that one of the shipping suppliers contracted with the platform is used. This is done by including it in the final invoice between the supplier and Emdad platform.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Copyright and intellectual rights of Emdad Platform Company:</strong> <br>
    •	Emdad Platform Company shall be committed to preserving the copyright and intellectual rights of all users of the platform.<br>
    •	All copyrights and intellectual rights of Emdad Platform Company shall be reserved. Violating the rights of Emdad Platform Company shall be strictly prohibited. In case of violation, the buyer shall face legal prosecution and accountability by official authorities.<br>
    •	It is strictly forbidden to copy, paste, use or reuse any content, services, or anything owned by of Emdad Platform Company.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Governance issues and disputes:</strong> <br>
    Any dispute shall be subject to the jurisdiction of Kingdom of Saudi Arabia courts. Both parties (supplier and buyer) shall be obligated to the terms and conditions. In the event of a dispute, it shall be resolved amicably with the help of Emdad Platform Company. In the event that the dispute is not resolved, it shall be transferred to the judicial authority.<br>
    •	All parties (supplier and buyer) shall agree that Emdad platform Company shall have the right to make amendments or changes to its terms of use page at any time if the Emdad platform Company deems it necessary.<br>
    •	It is strictly forbidden to use any services provided by Emdad Platform Company for any illegal or unethical purposes or any matters inconsistent with the Islamic Sharia.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Warranties and guarantees:</strong> <br>
    You acknowledge and guarantee that you shall:<br>
    •	Comply with all applicable laws and regulations in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.<br>
    •	Provide correct and accurate information to Emdad Platform Company and updating this information continuously.<br>
    •	Review and comply with any notices sent by Emdad Platform Company regarding your use of its provided services.<br>
    •	Agree to the exchange of information between the two parties (supplier and buyer) within the platform regarding the executed process, evaluation and communication.<br>
    •	Not harm the service or the platform in any way.<br>
    •	Maintain the password of your account or any provide means of identification securely and confidentially.<br>
    •	Provide all evidence proving your identity and the accuracy of your information at the discretion of Emdad Platform Company.<br>
    •	Emdad Platform Company shall have the right to refuse to provide the service or to access the platform without reasons.<br>
    •	Disclaimer of Emdad Platform Company for any wrong use by our officially approved users.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Payments:</strong> <br>
    •	Emdad Platform Company shall have the right to impose new fees for using the platform or the service or both. If you decide to extend the imposition of new fees, users shall be informed of this and they shall be allowed to continue or terminate the contract after settling previously approved accounts and transactions.<br>
    •	The buyer shall pay the value of the services and purchase the account of Emdad Platform Company at the specified time and bear the legal responsibility resulting from the delay or non-payment of the value of services and purchases at the time agreed upon in the purchase order. Emdad Platform Company shall have the right to resort to the judicial authorities in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.<br>
    •	Emdad Platform Company shall be responsible for paying the financial fees to the supplier on time following the completion of the delivery process and the approval of receipt of the invoice.<br>
    •	Emdad Platform Company shall have the right to prohibit or exclude the (service buyer) or stop his trading activity in the event that the buyer fails to pay the due amounts on time within a maximum period of 5 days from the date of entitlement. This shall be waived if the request is not received by the supplier or if the request is canceled before the due date.<br>
    •	You acknowledge and agree to be honest to the process and so on. You shall agree that in the event that any fraud, manipulation or deception, or if any illegal practices or misrepresentation of the service are proven, in a way that directly or indirectly affects Emdad Platform Company, (such as trying to make agreements outside the platform after customers communicate through the platform,) you shall be subject to suspension of your services in the Emdad Platform Company. Emdad Platform Company shall have the right to claim compensation for all damages that have been caused or will result because of this fraud, manipulation or misuse.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Compensations:</strong> <br>
    Upon agreeing to the terms and conditions of using Emdad Platform Company, you agree not to harm Emdad Platform Company, its affiliates, its licensors, its officials, directors, other users and employees, and absolve them of their liability from any claims, costs, damages, losses, liabilities and expenses (including attorney fees and costs) arising from or associated with the following:<br>
    •	Your violation of any of the terms and conditions of Emdad Platform Company, any applicable law or regulations in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, whether or not indicated in these terms and conditions of use.<br>
    •	Your violation of any rights of third parties, including (supplier and buyer) that are organized and sponsored by the Emdad Platform Company.<br>
    •	Your use or misuse of the platform or the service.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Modifying services:</strong> <br>
    Emdad Platform Company shall have the right, at its sole discretion, to do the following at any time:<br>
    •	Change services or any related materials or suspend publishing their services.<br>
    •	Suspend its services, at its own will, replace or stop the services with the knowledge of both parties in advance.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Liability limits:</strong> <br>
    •	Emdad Platform Company shall not make any explicit or implicit guarantees regarding the provided services.<br>
    •	Emdad Platform Company shall not guarantee the accuracy, content, or timeline of the provided services or products. The service buyer shall have the right to verify the service or product before receipt with the evaluation of the supplier.<br>
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Legal responsibility:</strong> <br>
    •	Emdad Platform Company shall not be responsible for any damages resulting from the use of (or the inability to use) the platform.<br>
    •	Emdad Platform Company shall not bear, under any circumstances, any responsibility related to the health or quality of the provided product or service and its conformity with the required specifications. The service can be refused at the time of receipt if it does not meet the required specifications. The supplier shall be evaluated.
    Emdad Platform Company shall not accept responsibility for any acts, behavior, negligence, or all of the above, on the part of the supplier.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Account security and information privacy:</strong> <br>
    •	Your decision to bear sole responsibility for the privacy of the information and for its use by anyone else using your account, username, password, or your access credentials.<br>
    •	You also agree to notify the Emdad Platform Company if you become aware of any loss, theft, or unauthorized use of any password, username, IP address, or other methods of accessing account information.
</p>
<p class="text-justify m-2 p-2">
    <strong>Transactions outside the platform:</strong> <br>
    When using Emdad Platform Company to benefit from its services, you may correspond with or request a quote or service or participate in promotional offers provided by the supplier, advertisers or sponsors that offer its products or services through its direct link with the Emdad Platform Company. These links take you to engage directly outside the platform. This behavior is incorrect and improper. Emdad Platform Company aims at your success, so supporting it would help bringing in your success.
</p>
